import {
  Box,
  TextField,
  MenuItem,
  FormControl,
  Typography,
} from "@mui/material";
import { LoadingButton } from "@mui/lab";

const Register = () => {
  return (
    <Box
      component="div"
      sx={{
        display: "flex",
        flexDirection: "column",
        flexWrap: "wrap",
        width: "auto",
        border: ".1px solid black",
        borderRadius: ".3rem",
      }}
      mt={12}
      ml="auto"
      mr="auto"
      p={5}
      gap={2}
    >
      <Typography variant="h3" fontWeight="bold">
        Creare cont
      </Typography>
      <Box
        component="form"
        noValidate
        autoComplete="off"
        sx={{ display: "flex", flexDirection: "wrap", flexWrap: "wrap" }}
        gap={2}
      >
        <FormControl>
          <TextField type="text" label="Nume" variant="outlined" size="small" />
        </FormControl>
        <FormControl>
          <TextField
            type="email"
            label="Email"
            variant="outlined"
            size="small"
          />
        </FormControl>
        <FormControl>
          <TextField
            type="password"
            label="Parolă"
            variant="outlined"
            size="small"
          />
        </FormControl>
        <FormControl>
          <TextField
            type="password"
            label="Confirmare parolă"
            variant="outlined"
            size="small"
          />
        </FormControl>
        <FormControl>
          <TextField
            label="Sex"
            variant="outlined"
            select
            sx={{ width: 75 }}
            value=""
            size="small"
          >
            <MenuItem value=""></MenuItem>
            <MenuItem value="m">M</MenuItem>
            <MenuItem value="f">F</MenuItem>
          </TextField>
        </FormControl>
      </Box>
      <LoadingButton
        variant="contained"
        loadingPosition="center"
        sx={{ backgroundColor: "secondary.main" }}
      >
        Înregistrare
      </LoadingButton>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Register;
